<!-- ===================== WHY WORK WITH US ===================== -->
<section class="why_work_with overflow-hidden dark_bg">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="headint_sec">
      <h2 class="title_section text-center">Why Work With Us</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="wrap_why_work grid grid-cols-2">
      <div class="item_why_work text-center" data-show-down data-delay=".1">
        <div class="icon_why_work"><img src="/img/icons/why_work_1.svg" alt="" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="title_why_work">Senior In-House Designers</div>
        <div class="descr_why_work">No matter what projects you have in the pipeline, our team of in-house designers is ready to help. Our designers will collaborate with you in Figma and deliver implementation-ready assets according to your requirements.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="item_why_work text-center" data-show-down data-delay=".1">
        <div class="icon_why_work"><img src="/img/icons/why_work_4.svg" alt="" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="title_why_work">Quick Turnarounds</div>
        <div class="descr_why_work">Small design projects like a set of social media graphics or a conference banner are usually completed within 48 hours. Small web projects like a five-page site are usually completed within two weeks. Either way, we're fast!</div>
      </div>
      <div class="item_why_work text-center" data-show-down data-delay=".2">
        <div class="icon_why_work"><img src="/img/icons/why_work_5.svg" alt="" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="title_why_work">Reliable Support</div>
        <div class="descr_why_work">We'll add you to our Slack channel, so ping us anytime with design questions or urgent requests. We reply the same business day between 9am and 6pm EST!</div>
      </div>
      <div class="item_why_work text-center" data-show-down data-delay=".3">
        <div class="icon_why_work"><img src="/img/icons/why_work_6.svg" alt="" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="title_why_work">Easy Task Management</div>
        <div class="descr_why_work">We'll add you to our Asana board, so you can start adding your design projects right away. This approach works well for clients who use our services on an ongoing basis.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

